{"title":"php中判断一个时间是今天的时间","date":"2018-07-23T01:57:00.000Z","link":"post/158","categories":["Other"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:12:01.006Z","content":"<p>超级简单即<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">createtime &gt;(time()-3600*24)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>多想想会明白的，有时候是有点绕:expressionless:</p>\n","prev":{"title":"mybatis中的事务管理器 TransactionManager基础知识","link":"post/159"},"next":{"title":"git 添加文件未识别","link":"post/157"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/158/"}